  {% filter markdown %}
    <h1>Depth</h1>
    <p class="spirit-subhead">Spirit provides a systematic language for conveying depth using shadows. To invite interaction or increase prominence, animate a component along the Z axis to simulate depth.</p>
  {% endfilter %}
